generator

Class GaussDistribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • generator.GaussDistribution

  • public class GaussDistribution
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides acces to randomly generated data under normal Gauss distribution of probability. Default values and methods are prepared for specific generation of population in range between 100k - 10M people, but can be set for different scenario using non-simplified constructor. Class also provides generation of name for planet(population). Those names are generated for "line". Names on the same line are diferent by 3 last digit of the name. Lines are labeled by 2 characters before numbers.
    Author:
    Martin Hamet 7.10.2015

        public GaussDistribution(int samples,
                         double centerPoint)

        centerPoint - value with highest probability
